{"id": "26826", "post": "<div class=\"post-26826 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-editorial tag-dedi tag-kvm tag-lowendtalk tag-shared-hosting tag-vps\" id=\"post-26826\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/lowendtalk-offers-weekly-roundup-april-24-2021/\" rel=\"bookmark\">LowEndTalk Offers Weekly Roundup (April 24, 2021)</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/dedi/\" rel=\"tag\">dedi</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/kvm/\" rel=\"tag\">kvm</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/lowendtalk/\" rel=\"tag\">lowendtalk</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/shared-hosting/\" rel=\"tag\">shared hosting</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/vps/\" rel=\"tag\">VPS</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> April 24, 2021 @ 7:36 pm, by raindog308</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/lowendtalk-roundup-1-300x300.png.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-26734 alignright litespeed-loaded\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/lowendtalk-roundup-1-300x300.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" align=\"right\" hspace=\"20\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/lowendtalk-roundup-1.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/lowendtalk-roundup-1-150x150.png.webp 150w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/lowendtalk-roundup-1.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/lowendtalk-roundup-1-150x150.png.webp 150w\" data-was-processed=\"true\"></p><p><em>We feature many great offers here on LowEndBox, but you\u2019ll also find some unique provider postings on our sister site, <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">LowEndTalk</a>.&nbsp; If you\u2019re in the market for great hosting, be sure to check both sites.&nbsp; Here\u2019s a summary of what offers have been posted on <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">LowEndTalk</a> this week!</em></p><p>PulsedMedia brought us some more fantastic <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/171204/pulsed-media-value1000-seedboxes-third-times-the-charm-1gbps-raid0-seedboxes-at-best-prices\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">seedboxes</a>.</p><p>DediPath celebrated setting up shop in Dallas with a great <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/171187/dedipath-is-now-open-in-the-infomart-building-in-dallas\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">SSD VPS offer</a>.</p><p>Get <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/171202/cloud-vps-in-singapore-from-3-68-centos-debian-ubuntu-windows\">Cloud VPS in Singapore from $3.68</a> from JustVPS.</p><p>You can get an <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/171181/crowncloud-amd-ryzen-9-5950x-kvm-at-los-angeles-starting-at-5-month-more\">AMD Ryzen KVMs in LA starting at $5/month</a>&nbsp;from CrownCloud.</p><p>HappyBee Host has OpenVZ VMs <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/171157/happybee-host-vps-starting-at-1-mo-openvz-7-kvm\">starting at $1/mo</a>.</p><p>Little Creek Hosting <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/171105/starting-at-3-50-kvm-virtualizor-nvme-24-7-support\">has KVMs starting at $3.50</a> with 24/7 support.</p><p>Ginernet <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/171191/ginernet-kvm-1-core-1gb-ram-10gb-nvme-10gbps-spain-madrid-interxion\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">posted 1GB VMs in Spain</a> for us.</p><p>RackNerd announced <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/171093/racknerd-is-rapidly-growing-amd-ryzen-vps-now-available-in-seattle\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Ryzen VPSes</a> in Seattle.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/171185/interserver-dedicated-servers-starting-at-49-per-month\">InterServer shared dedicated servers starting at $49 per month</a>.</p><p>MivoCloud offered <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/171176/nvme-dedicated-server-in-europe-own-data-center-support-24-7-uptime-99-9\">NVMe Dedicated Servers</a>.</p><p>WiredBlade has <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/171126/us-phx-wiredblade-vps-100-nvme-ssd-4-gb-ram-2-cpu-40-gb-nvme-ssd-10-gbps-uplink-5-mo\">4 GB RAM/2 CPU/40 GB NVMe SSD</a> VMs for $5/mo.</p><p>Hosterlabs offered you&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/171107/42-0-off-on-all-our-product-lines-promo-code-420-happy-420-to-you-all\">42.0% off on all our product lines</a> (to celebrate 4/20).</p><p>BACloud has&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/171156/single-and-dual-e5-25-off-customize-cpu-ram-ssds-vps-nl-lt-usa-15-recurring-off\">Single and DUAL E5s for 25% OFF</a>.</p><p>Hitch up with <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/171137/datawagon-instant-setup-dedicated-servers-from-39-new-york-chicago-ddos-protection\">DataWagon and get a dedicated server for only $39 in New York or Chicago</a>.</p><p>1GServers has <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/171147/1gservers-com-dual-e5-dedicated-specials-tata-now-live-phoenix-arizona-usa-usa-west\">dual E5 dedicated specials in Phoenix, Arizona</a>.</p><p>In the Netherlands, you can get triple the bandwidth and eightfold the IPs at<a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/171072/nl-dedicated-server-deals-triple-the-bandwidth-eightfold-the-ips-and-half-the-price\"> half the price</a>&nbsp;from HostSlick</p><p>Inception posted <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/171108/inception-hosting-kvm-netherlands-amsterdam-buy-before-you-try\">KVMs in the Netherlands</a> for us.</p><p>AlphaVPS posted an <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/171086/are-you-looking-for-a-reliable-and-fast-vps-we-have-some-amd-epyc-servers-available\">EPYC offer</a>.</p><p>HostNamaste has <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/171085/kvm-storage-vps-in-us-at-30-year-and-openvz-7-vps-in-canada-at-20-year-hostnamaste\">KVM storage VPSes in the US starting at $30/year</a> and more.</p><p>EntryBytes is <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/171069/entrybytes-we-make-affordable-sexy-packed-with-family-perks-us-nyc-miami-la-nl-naaldwijk\">making affordable sexy in NYC/MIAMI/LA/NL</a>.</p><p>LeapSwitch posted an offer for VMs in <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/171053/mumbai-india-usa-germany-portugal-spain-2gb-ram-1-core-30gb-ssd-5\">India, USA, Germany, Portugal, and Spain</a>.</p><div class=\"relpost-thumb-wrapper\"><div class=\"relpost-thumb-container\"><h3>Related posts:</h3><div style=\"clear: both\"></div><div style=\"clear: both\"></div><div class=\"relpost-block-container\"><a class=\"relpost-block-single\" href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/providers-partner-with-lowendbox-2/\"><div class=\"relpost-custom-block-single\" style=\"width: 150px; height: 215px;\"><div class=\"relpost-block-single-image\" alt=\"Providers: Partner with LowEndBox!\" style=\"background: transparent url(https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/lowendbox_promo-150x150.png) no-repeat scroll 0% 0%; width: 150px; height: 150px;\"></div><div class=\"relpost-block-single-text\" style=\"font-family: Arial;  font-size: 12px;  color: #333333;\">Providers: Partner with LowEndBox!</div></div></a><a class=\"relpost-block-single\" href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/hostbastic-for-the-price-of-a-cup-of-coffee-host-for-a-year-with-directadmin-in-singapore-london-usa/\"><div class=\"relpost-custom-block-single\" style=\"wid